---
import LegalLayout from "@/layouts/LegalLayout.astro"
---

<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    Kobbe is built with privacy at its core. We collect only the minimum
    information necessary to operate the service. This policy explains what
    we collect, how it's used, and the choices you have.
  </p>

  <h2>What Kobbe does not collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No cookies or localStorage identifiers</li>
    <li>No raw IP addresses (IPs are never stored)</li>
    <li>No personal profiles or cross-session tracking</li>
    <li>No fingerprinting</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>
    When you visit a site that uses Kobbe, the following anonymous,
    aggregated data may be collected:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Page URL (path only, no query parameters with personal data)</li>
    <li>Referrer domain (not the full URL)</li>
    <li>Browser and device type</li>
    <li>Country (derived from request metadata, not IP geolocation databases)</li>
    <li>Custom event names (if configured by the site owner)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use your data</h2>
  <p>We use collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Display aggregate traffic statistics on the site owner's dashboard</li>
    <li>Filter bot and spam traffic</li>
    <li>Improve the product</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing and disclosure</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell data. Analytics data is only visible to the site owner
    (and anyone they share a public dashboard link with). We may disclose
    information if required by law.
  </p>

  <h2>Data storage</h2>
  <p>
    Data is stored on Cloudflare infrastructure in the site owner's own
    account. Retention policies are configured by the site owner.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    Because Kobbe does not collect personal data or use cookies, GDPR
    consent banners are not required. If you have questions about how a
    specific site uses Kobbe, contact the site owner directly.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy from time to time. The most recent revision
    date will be noted at the top of this page.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this Privacy Policy can be sent to
    <a href="mailto:privacy@kobbe.io">privacy@kobbe.io</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
